          <mainBody>
            <p><span style="color:#0070C0"><b>Annex B - Territorial extent and application in the United Kingdom</b></span></p>
            <blockContainer>
              <num>66 </num>
              <p><span style="color:#000000">The Trade (Comprehensive and Progressive Agreement for Trans-Pacific Partnership) Act extends to the whole of the UK except for section 3(4)(a) and Part 1 (amendments to procurement regulations for England and Wales and Northern Ireland) and section 3(4)(b) and Part 2 of the Schedule (amendments to procurement regulations for Scotland). </span></p>
            </blockContainer>
            <p><span style="color:#000000">The information provided is the view of the UK Government.</span></p>
